  "text": "You can understand why patients need education (or re-education) early, to deal with anxieties and frustrations in returning to work. [CITATION_1] Such an approach may simply require some straightforward, \"no nonsense\" advice, as presented in previous publications. 14 28 5 Avoid letting the stress of dealing with litigation and insurance people cause more muscle tension. 6 Do not pay too much attention and worry over every new ache and pain or symptom. 7 Do not wear a collar. 8 Do not rely on medications rather than activity to \"heal\" the injury.",
